Woah.

792
00:53:28,204 --> 00:53:30,248
-Go straight, go straight.
-Wow.

793
00:53:32,584 --> 00:53:33,627
I think I did it.

794
00:53:34,002 --> 00:53:35,462
Okay.

795
00:53:35,545 --> 00:53:37,130
Let's try that again, slowly.

796
00:53:37,797 --> 00:53:39,341
