with a straight face?

812
00:54:13,500 --> 00:54:14,751
Let's try that again.

813
00:54:14,834 --> 00:54:15,877
-Let's not.
-I can do this.

814
00:54:15,961 --> 00:54:17,087
-No…
-I'll give it a go.

815
00:54:17,170 --> 00:54:19,381
-Let's take a break.
-Left, left…

816
00:54:20,590 --> 00:54:23,218
Your probation officer…

817
00:54:24,219 --> 00:54:25,261
Ro-eum.

818
00:54:27,931 --> 00:54:28,807
Hi.

819
00:54:36,064 --> 00:54:37,273
Lee Ro-eum…

820
00:54:53,164 --> 00:54:54,374
We're in love.

821
00:54:55,959 --> 00:54:58,670
I thought you had a lot of free time.
Looks like you've been busy.

822
00:55:00,922 --> 00:55:04,384
The recovery team
for Navis Well-being's criminal proceeds

823
00:55:04,467 --> 00:55:06,094
are continuing to expand.

824
00:55:06,177 --> 00:55:09,764
They are working on laws
to back up legal procedures

825
00:55:09,848 --> 00:55:11,933
and hiring digital and financial experts…

826
00:55:13,435 --> 00:55:14,436
Me?

827
00:55:14,519 --> 00:55:15,395
Yes.

828
00:55:15,979 --> 00:55:17,731
We need your help.

829
00:55:18,648 --> 00:55:19,983
We're bringing in people

830
00:55:20,066 --> 00:55:22,736
from the cybercrimes unit
and the criminal proceeds recovery team,

831
00:55:22,819 --> 00:55:26,990
but no one knows as much as you do
about the mechanism of Red Eye.

832
00:55:27,073 --> 00:55:29,242
Your joining the team won't be disclosed,

833
00:55:29,325 --> 00:55:31,244
and you'll receive protection too.

834
00:55:31,327 --> 00:55:33,288
You'll be part of a special task force.

835
00:55:35,957 --> 00:55:37,959
After all, con artists know best

836
00:55:39,461 --> 00:55:40,545
about scams.

837
00:55:52,432 --> 00:55:54,184
You should do it if you want to.

838
00:55:55,810 --> 00:55:56,978
What do you think?

839
00:55:57,687 --> 00:55:58,897
I guess you want to.

840
00:56:00,148 --> 00:56:02,650
I never told you
why I joined Red Eye, did I?

841
00:56:11,117 --> 00:56:13,745
It was the first place
that had acknowledged me.

842
00:56:14,788 --> 00:56:16,122
So-dam was sick,

843
00:56:16,790 --> 00:56:18,666
my parents were busy working,

844
00:56:18,750 --> 00:56:21,086
and I was always alone,
at home and at school.

845
00:56:21,169 --> 00:56:23,296
They were the first to praise what I did.

846
00:56:26,216 --> 00:56:27,967
How simple-minded and stupid of me.

847
00:56:28,927 --> 00:56:30,678
I often thought about whether

848
00:56:31,387 --> 00:56:34,265
things would've been different if it
hadn't been Red Eye but somewhere else.

849
00:56:35,517 --> 00:56:37,811
Just do it if you want to.
Don't think too much about it.

850
00:56:38,603 --> 00:56:39,521
It just feels like

851
00:56:40,438 --> 00:56:42,649
I'm the only one who can't let go

852
00:56:42,732 --> 00:56:43,650
of the past.

853
00:56:44,192 --> 00:56:46,027
It sounds like responsibility to me.

854
00:56:46,111 --> 00:56:48,696
If you have the skills
and a good sense of responsibility,

855
00:56:49,656 --> 00:56:52,534
do what's good for society.
And receive the recognition you deserve.

856
00:56:53,159 --> 00:56:54,160
What about you?

857
00:56:54,244 --> 00:56:55,203
What about me?

858
00:56:55,286 --> 00:56:57,664
I think Mr. Ryu has you in mind too.

859
00:57:01,459 --> 00:57:03,545
I'm going to live a nice, boring life.

860
00:57:03,628 --> 00:57:05,046
I don't want to be bothered.

861
00:57:37,370 --> 00:57:39,122
I've been wondering,

862
00:57:40,498 --> 00:57:41,875
what's always so funny?

863
00:57:41,958 --> 00:57:43,626
Bring Ro-eum to me.

864
00:57:44,711 --> 00:57:46,921
As long as you're alive,
that'll never happen.

865
00:57:47,005 --> 00:57:49,799
I'll be out in a few years.

866
00:57:50,633 --> 00:57:52,260
That won't happen either.

867
00:57:52,969 --> 00:57:54,596
Try to appeal all you want.

868
00:57:55,638 --> 00:57:58,975
Even without the cases
where the statute of limitations ran out,

869
00:57:59,058 --> 00:58:01,394
you'll be on one tedious trial
after another.

870
00:58:01,478 --> 00:58:02,520
Even in your dreams,

871
00:58:02,604 --> 00:58:03,730
and even after you die.

872
00:58:04,689 --> 00:58:05,982
You came to tell me that?

873
00:58:06,065 --> 00:58:07,400
One more thing.

874
00:58:08,359 --> 00:58:09,736
Whatever cheap, dirty way

875
00:58:09,819 --> 00:58:12,989
you're thinking of using,

876
00:58:13,072 --> 00:58:14,741
you better not come near us.

877
00:58:14,824 --> 00:58:15,867
Or what?

878
00:58:16,367 --> 00:58:18,244
Unlike Ro-eum,

879
00:58:18,328 --> 00:58:20,580
I don't care if you live or die.

880
00:58:22,832 --> 00:58:25,335
Letting you live wasn't a mistake.

881
00:58:39,891 --> 00:58:40,975
I'm sorry.

882
00:58:43,728 --> 00:58:46,689
I didn't really think about
how you were a living, breathing person

883
00:58:48,525 --> 00:58:49,567
like me.

884
00:58:51,903 --> 00:58:53,029
So back then…

885
00:58:54,572 --> 00:58:56,115
I had no sense of guilt.

886
00:58:57,867 --> 00:58:59,869
If it weren't
for the statute of limitations,

887
00:59:00,620 --> 00:59:03,373
I'd be in prison too for scamming you.

888
00:59:05,375 --> 00:59:06,918
It's not your fault.

889
00:59:08,753 --> 00:59:10,922
It's the people who made you
do it that are the monsters.

890
00:59:19,430 --> 00:59:20,640
I'm sorry.

891
00:59:23,393 --> 00:59:24,978
Every single day for ten years,

892
00:59:25,061 --> 00:59:26,271
I had the same dream.

893
00:59:29,148 --> 00:59:30,358
About that night.

894
00:59:33,236 --> 00:59:35,863
So I know how horrible that feels.

895
00:59:40,702 --> 00:59:41,661
I wanted…

896
00:59:43,538 --> 00:59:46,040
to tell you that you should
sleep more easily now.

897
00:59:49,460 --> 00:59:50,587
I can sleep…

898
00:59:52,672 --> 00:59:54,215
easily now too.

899
00:59:55,216 --> 00:59:57,010
Thanks to Attorney Han.

