01:00:11,399 --> 01:00:14,902
A year since the arrest of Lee Jay,
the mastermind of Navis,

902
01:00:14,986 --> 01:00:19,032
a total of 42 people have been indicted
for their crimes related to

903
01:00:19,115 --> 01:00:20,992
Red Eye and Navis,

904
01:00:21,075 --> 01:00:23,578
and nine have been sentenced.

