01:00:23,661 --> 01:00:27,290
Lee Jay is still embroiled
in over 30 suits,

906
01:00:27,373 --> 01:00:30,627
with more time being added
to his sentence with each trial.

907
01:00:50,813 --> 01:00:52,607
Thank you.

908
01:00:56,027 --> 01:00:57,487
For having

909
01:00:59,489 --> 01:01:00,782
a daughter like me.

910
01:01:12,168 --> 01:01:13,544
This is all we have.

911
01:01:13,628 --> 01:01:14,671
Is it okay?

912
01:01:24,764 --> 01:01:25,890
Zero?

913
01:01:26,933 --> 01:01:28,059
Not bad.

914
01:01:29,018 --> 01:01:29,977
Here.

915
01:01:31,979 --> 01:01:34,649
Check the revisions and sign.

916
01:01:46,160 --> 01:01:52,083
SIGN: LEE RO-EUM

917
01:01:52,709 --> 01:01:53,835
Here too.

918
01:01:58,464 --> 01:02:00,174
Once I send the money,

919
01:02:00,883 --> 01:02:01,759
that'll be it?

920
01:02:03,302 --> 01:02:05,054
Yes, that's it. For you and me.

921
01:02:12,145 --> 01:02:13,062
For this contract.

922
01:02:16,858 --> 01:02:19,026
You better not need a lawyer again.

923
01:02:26,159 --> 01:02:27,076
Na-sa.

924
01:02:27,160 --> 01:02:28,536
Where are the cable ties?

925
01:02:28,619 --> 01:02:30,288
Over here.

926
01:02:31,539 --> 01:02:32,707
Hey, Ro-eum.

927
01:02:32,790 --> 01:02:34,584
I think you've been scammed.

928
01:02:34,667 --> 01:02:37,378
The lights may look nice,
but have you seen the second floor?

929
01:02:37,462 --> 01:02:40,089
All the bathroom tiles are broken,
and the doors don't close properly.

930
01:02:40,173 --> 01:02:41,507
Stop talking and work.

931
01:02:42,925 --> 01:02:45,470
Ask the owner to fix it up.

932
01:02:45,553 --> 01:02:47,221
Can't you just fix it now?

933
01:02:47,305 --> 01:02:49,474
I am. What does it look like I'm doing?

934
01:02:49,557 --> 01:02:53,102
I'm saying she should charge
for the repairs and not be a pushover.

935
01:02:54,353 --> 01:02:55,688
Is Moo-young coming?

936
01:02:56,105 --> 01:02:57,106
No.

937
01:02:58,608 --> 01:03:00,318
You didn't tell him you were moving?

938
01:03:01,194 --> 01:03:02,028
No.

939
01:03:02,445 --> 01:03:03,446
Do I need to?

940
01:03:11,162 --> 01:03:12,705
Okay, okay, okay.

