976
01:04:49,218 --> 01:04:50,136
You're busy?

977
01:04:50,636 --> 01:04:51,804
Doing what?

978
01:04:51,888 --> 01:04:53,306
Moving.

979
01:04:53,389 --> 01:04:54,724
Oh, you're moving.

980
01:04:54,807 --> 01:04:55,850
Good for you.

981
01:04:55,933 --> 01:04:57,226
Are you moving alone?

982
01:04:57,310 --> 01:04:58,519
Do you have help?

983
01:04:58,603 --> 01:04:59,687
I do.

984
01:05:09,322 --> 01:05:10,448
Wow.

985
01:05:11,949 --> 01:05:13,117
Nice place.

986
01:05:14,493 --> 01:05:16,078
